parameters:
Thief Nora: It's really strange... I can breathe even though
I'm underwater. It feels weird!

Mage Relm: The biggest drawback of the magical device, which
literally has a low burden on the crystal, is its tendency
to gather living beings.

Mage Relm: This air outfit won't last long. Let's quickly
get the red coral reef and return!

Priestess Sophia: Colorful corals... I wanted to try
drinking wine here.

Clea: It seems like it will take more time to go up using
the anchor chain than to descend.
Mage Relm: Hehe, in case of emergency, I'll use my magic--

Thief Nora: A loud crashing sound... Everyone, it's coming
from the ship!
Thief Nora: Something is falling from above!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
